%I A397795 #8 Jul 13 2026 08:18:14
%S A397795 0,1,8,40,88,8,104,56,40,16
%N A397795 Numerator of the maximum expected number of steps of a knight's random walk on an infinite chessboard before it lands on a mined square, given that all but n squares are mined.
%F A397795 For 1 <= n <= 9, the maximum expected number of steps is a(n)/A397796(n) = 8*(n+7)/(65-n). This is attained by sweeping the starting square together with n-1 of the 8 squares reachable in one knight's move.
%Y A397795 Cf. A326954, A366998, A397796 (denominators).
%K A397795 nonn,frac,hard,more,new
